$ HTML element: canvas

Draw graphics onto a HTML page with → development/languages/JavaScript.
-
There are two APIs with which graphics can be rendered onto a `<canvas>` element:
  • → development/web/HTML/tags/canvas/API
  • → https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API[WebGL API] (See also → development/web/WebGL and the → development/web/WebGL/OpenGL-ES-Shading-Language/WebGL2RenderingContext[`WebGLRenderingContext` and `WebGL2RenderingContext` interfaces])

